</blockquote>
<h2 data-start="4159" data-end="4208"><strong>A Deeper Connection — Nature &amp; Spirituality</strong></h2>
<p data-start="4210" data-end="4451">This valley is not only about flowers — it’s about <em data-start="4261" data-end="4278">faith and peace</em>. Locals believe the Pandavas once performed penance for Sati Savitri here. The air, the soil, and the silence all carry a divine energy that transforms everyone who visits.</p><h2 data-start="4458" data-end="4506"><strong>Trekking Safety &amp; Guidelines (2025 Rules)</strong></h2>
<ol data-start="4508" data-end="4749">
 	<li data-start="4508" data-end="4546">
<p data-start="4511" data-end="4546">Daily trek limit: 300 trekkers</p>
</li>
 	<li data-start="4547" data-end="4601">
<p data-start="4550" data-end="4601">Be cautious of reduced oxygen above 10,000 ft</p>
</li>
 	<li data-start="4602" data-end="4650">
<p data-start="4605" data-end="4650">Rain gear is mandatory during June–July</p>
</li>
 	<li data-start="4651" data-end="4704">
<p data-start="4654" data-end="4704">Strict ban on plastic and smoking in the park</p>
</li>
 	<li data-start="4651" data-end="4704">
<p data-start="4654" data-end="4704">Carry lightweight bags and rain covers</p>
</li>
</ol>
